                <li>Improve exterior entrance security at all campuses.</li>
            </ul>
            <p class="mb-0 ff-bb">Phase 3:</p>
            <ul>
                <li>Replace and repair parking lots, sidewalks, and curbing</li>
                <li>Purchase buses throughout as needed</li>
            </ul>
